{"tid":391965,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【LIVE】中大學生會就「香港獨立橫額事件」圍堵學生事務處","createTime":"2017-09-08T07:28:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-08T11:06:16.000Z","uid":79563,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3eb6703b6c598dd2940351f986c643beb636773c","tid":391965,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T07:28:48.000Z","msg":"LINK: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkucampustv/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkucampustv%2F&d=hZxFouYXqEcKQXDZPuqUTBxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=60a46c10\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkucampustv/</a><br />\n<br />\n【現場直播】學界圍堵中大學生事務處<br />\n<br />\n針對近日中大校方打壓校內有關港獨的言論，學界於今日（九月八日）下午約二時三十分發起圍堵中大學生事務處之行動。是次行動有兩大訴求，第一：校方不會再就同學表達之意見作政治審查，打壓同學的言論自由；第二：校方不會再強行清拆由學生會管理之場地内的宣傳品，歸還學生自治權。現場約有四十人，包括香港中文大學學生會、香港大學學生會、香港城市大學學生會、香港浸會大學學生會、香港教育大學學生會以及香港樹仁大學學生會之幹事。<br />\n<br />\n(15:03) 中大學生事務處處長梁汝照稱要「打電話」，中大學生會幹事現在門口等待。<br />\n<br />\n(15:13) 有保安來到學生事務處，有中大同學稱有名保安曾打過中大的同學，要求梁汝照叫該名保安離開。梁稱已找副校長和學生對談，並會於下午四時半在預約了的房間進行，中大幹事回應事務處已是適合的地方。"},{"pid":"f1c4bf33fabb3b7c6e8e1a6d594a582d7c3209c1","tid":391965,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T07:29:27.000Z","msg":"【民主牆上出現以共產黨黨旗為背景海報】<br />\n<br />\n根據香港大學學生會學苑即時新聞昨晚的報道，原張貼在民主牆上的「香港獨立」字句於昨午被人撕走。本台於今日（九月七日）早上十一時五十分拍攝到民主牆前的玻璃門仍未關上，但被撕下的紙張已被移走。下午一時零八分，民主牆上出現白底黑字印上「香港獨立 支援中大學生會」的字句。晚上八時五十五分，民主牆上出現一張簡體字的海報，上面印上「沒有甚麼是馬克思主義 不能解決的 如果有 就是沒有結合 中國特色社會主義」，以及三張以共產黨黨旗為背景的海報，而該海報亦遮蓋原張貼在民主牆上「支援中大學生會」的字句。<br />\n<br />\n根據香港大學學生會內務守則甲部第九部分，指出使用民主牆時不可遮蓋未過期之張貼品，以及只有幹事會有權清除任何違規張貼品而不作保存及事前通知。"},{"pid":"90c487bdd1092731f81233e17ba16d192c104b6d","tid":391965,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T07:31:45.000Z","msg":"2人 VS &gt; 50 人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s26.postimg.org/53unxfo89/CUHK_HKI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs26.postimg.org%2F53unxfo89%2FCUHK_HKI.jpg&h=ca64c4f4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fcefd2f160f690801cf5b1912954805b8ba2dd75","tid":391965,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T07:33:08.000Z","msg":"互相辯論中....<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s26.postimg.org/yx1o61cvd/CUHK_HKI2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs26.postimg.org%2Fyx1o61cvd%2FCUHK_HKI2.jpg&h=39fc7cde&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89665e1a7295ecf76347ad7cb64b4474d47d1125","tid":391965,"uid":28366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T07:39:36.000Z","msg":"【香港中文大學學生會被捕支援 - Legal Aid Provided by the CUSU In Case of Arrest】<br />\n<br />\n今日兩時半開始「堅守言論自由，還我學生自治」圍堵行動，同學現正圍堵本部范克廉樓一樓學生事務處辦公室，要求校方與本會公開面談並回應訴求，還中大同學一個有言論自由、思想自由的校園。本會呼籲出席同學注意安全，若不幸被捕或知道有人被捕，請將被捕者以下資料告知我們:<br />\n1. 中英文全名<br />\n2. 性別<br />\n3. 就讀科目及年級<br />\n4. 身份證號碼<br />\n5. 電話號碼<br />\n6. 正前往之警署(如適用)<br />\n同學可<br />\n1. 致電6022-5269以聯絡學生會幹事<br />\n2. 發訊息到Telegram: CUSU1718<br />\n3. PM 本專頁<br />\n<br />\nIf any student or your friend is heading to the site and would like to obtain legal aid in case of arrest, please send us the following information-<br />\n1. Full name (in Chinese and English)<br />\n2. Gender<br />\n3. Curriculum and Year<br />\n4. HKID No.<br />\n5. Phone No.<br />\n6. The police station you are heading to (if applicable)<br />\nYou may<br />\n1. Dial 6022-5269 to contact our executive committee member<br />\n2. Send you message through Telegram to CUSU1718<br />\n3. PM our Facebook page"},{"pid":"4911355e65d0874b23b5a8e77642c67b8b3d951d","tid":391965,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T08:06:25.000Z","msg":"成村人一人一句輪緊學生事務處 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6aad3f7b0c4c126134639a8c72c4e019c6d7259","tid":391965,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T09:39:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"042e9d9f6efd4a84d7af16f68b4668f61575f322","tid":391965,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T09:40:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f57f1b855bb746e75d08f047c419f632ca302b3","tid":391965,"uid":15356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T09:41:34.000Z","msg":"加油呀 唔好兩秒就比人抬走"},{"pid":"80a1f43b43796c3689cebb3af3e4101f1faa0eff","tid":391965,"uid":22210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T09:48:51.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"e8d39123ba67160a37f6a23c40030556b56acc0b","tid":391965,"uid":60158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T09:54:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c7acb6154e9035d5ee3cb56bef89b8eb52bbbffe","tid":391965,"uid":90183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T09:56:12.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"af5f8882a17472e9a44628321f4144adef99f1ef","tid":391965,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T10:01:10.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aa0a7902d49a1cb3d3b72c83e9df222e8a4f19f","tid":391965,"uid":60749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T10:04:58.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4503129ba6c80a84d8c86b3fc805c5a4f6b4b0c9","tid":391965,"uid":81627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T10:13:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8702e038c151912b165c4d129c0c57d613d04cf","tid":391965,"uid":110019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T10:34:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6be4094a13645a2c3fa29c24c87f13be4949486","tid":391965,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T1